title: Zakhmi Aurat
subTitle: Determined to exact revenge on the goons who gangraped her, Inspector Kiran Dutt, takes matters into her own hands as the law fails to give her justice.

title: Baat Bann Gayi
subTitle: Kabir falls in love with Rachna, but he must impress her brother, Professor Laxmi Nivas, to get her hand in marriage. Things turn upside down when his lookalike shows up.

title: Baadshah
subTitle: An amateur detective, Raj, goes by the nickname of Baadshah. But this name soon causes a misunderstanding that lands him in the middle of a conspiracy to assassinate the chief minister of Goa.

title: Aakhri Ghulam
subTitle: Bheema and his family live under the tyranny of their master, Daulat Singh. But, when Bheema revolts, his love for his master's daughter is threatened.

title: Juaari
subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Zafar's obsessive love for Salma leads to her separation from her son, Iqbal. Twenty years later, Iqbal strives to reunite with his mother.

title: Bol Radha Bol
subTitle: While Kishen enjoys village life and romance with Radha, a sinister doppelganger plots. Upon returning home, he'll discover his identity and life stolen by this malevolent impostor.

title: Khel
subTitle: Three fraudsters trick a rich elderly woman, Sulakshana, who is desperately looking for her long-lost grandchild, in order to acquire her estate and property.

title: Khel
subTitle: Three fraudsters trick a rich elderly woman, Sulakshana, who is desperately looking for her long-lost grandchild, in order to acquire her estate and property.

title: Lashkar
subTitle: Professor Anand's life changes dramatically when Sangram Singh murders his family and assaults his sister. Devastated, Anand decides to seek revenge with Inspector Sumeet's help.

title: Keemat
subTitle: After two thugs accidentally kill a man, they hide the truth from his family and try to save his village from the torments of an evil landlord in order to redeem themselves.

title: Pyar Ke Kabil
subTitle: Twin siblings are kept apart from each other after their parents separate. However, years later, the twins reunite and decide to switch roles in order to bring their parents back together.

title: Kahani Kismat Ki
subTitle: After his release from jail, a criminal tries to make an honest living. However, his plans go awry when a woman claims that he is her husband and later he is arrested for murder.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.

title: Saathi
subTitle: Two boys are left to fend for themselves after their father falls victim to police brutality. They make a living through petty crimes, but things get out of hand when they cross paths with an underworld kingpin.

title: Chaalbaaz
subTitle: Anju endures mistreatment at home, whereas her long-separated twin Manju boldly navigates life's challenges. By some quirk of fate, they end up trading places, and their worlds erupt in chaos.

title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Chalte Chalte
subTitle: Geeta is admitted to a psychiatric hospital after her lover passes away tragically. Later, she gains her senses, only to find him alive and in love with another woman.

title: Main Intequam Loonga
subTitle: Kumar learns that his father, a national level boxing champion, was killed when he refused to lose a fight. He vows to annihilate his father's killers, unaware that he may face tragic consequences.

title: Khel Khilari Ka
subTitle: Ajit swears revenge after witnessing his family's murder by three thugs. Years later, he becomes a wealthy crime lord, but he still thirsts for revenge.

title: Katilon Ke Kaatil
subTitle: Traumatised by her murder of her husband and the abduction of her two sons, a woman spends her life looking for her family. Things take a turn when two men arrive at her house with a family heirloom.

title: Prithvi
subTitle: When Prithvi and Neha, a newly-wed couple, travel abroad for their honeymoon, Neha goes missing. Later, he fights against all odds to rescue her.

title: Prem Deewane
subTitle: A young couple in love run away together after their parents oppose their relationship. They are misguided into kidnapping a wealthy person for a big ransom by a shrewd uncle who has his own agenda.

title: Ganga Tere Desh Mein
subTitle: After arresting and institutionalising a notorious criminal who has lost his mental faculties, inspector Ajay finds his mother feeding the criminal. But when he digs deeper he uncovers a tragic truth.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.
